Check Installed NVIDIA Packages

To inspect installed NVIDIA-related packages:

Command:
    rpm -qa | grep -i nvidia

This showed that NVIDIA 595.80 packages were installed, including:
- akmod-nvidia
- xorg-x11-drv-nvidia
- xorg-x11-drv-nvidia-libs
- xorg-x11-drv-nvidia-cuda-libs
- kmod-nvidia for kernel 7.1.3

These packages were incompatible with GTX 750 Ti.
